sql:
SELECT value
FROM stock_metadata
WHERE key = 'CEO';

external_knowledge:
- A "sector average close price" refers to the average closing price of all stocks within a particular sector; 
- "Cumulative volume by industry" refers to the total volume of all stocks within an industry, listed in order from highest to lowest based on company name; 
- "User access count" refers to the number of times each stock has been accessed by users, and "last access date" refers to the most recent date each stock was accessed.
